132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST SPECIAL SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 1322
H.P. 857 House of Representatives, March 27, 2025
Resolve, to Establish a Pilot Program to Enhance Youth Hunting
Participation
Reference to the Committee on Inland Fisheries and Wildlife suggested and ordered
printed.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
Presented by Representative ROBERTS of South Berwick.
Cosponsored by Senator GUERIN of Penobscot and
Representatives: BRIDGEO of Augusta, CLUCHEY of Bowdoinham, COLLAMORE of
